#include <iostream>
#include <string>
#include <map>
 #include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
 
int main() {
	int N,q,l;
	string s;
	long long v;
	map<long long,string>m;
	cin>>N;
	for(int i=0;i<N;i++){
	   cin>>s>>v;
	   m[v]=s;
	}
	cin>>q;
	map<long long,string>::reverse_iterator rit;
	for(int i=0;i<q;i++){
	    cin>>s;
	    l=s.length();
	    for(rit=m.rbegin();rit!=m.rend();rit++){
	        if(rit->second.substr(0,l)==s){
	            cout<<rit->second<<endl;
	            break;
	        }
	    }
	    if(rit==m.rend())
	    cout<<"NO"<<endl;
	}
	return 0;
}
